<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>696</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 rén de shēng mìng hé děng duǎn zàn, rú fēng rú yún, rú huā rú yān.
 tiān jiā nián nián jìn nǎ, shì jiè rì rì yuǎn. wǒ men yī tóng huí jiā, yǒu hěn duō hěn duō tóng bàn.
 zhǔ yǐn dǎo wǒ men zǒu hé shì de lù, suí zǒu suí chuán. yī lù duō bēn máng, yī lù duō áo liàn.
 jiàn dào tiān fù miàn nǎ, tā yào gào sù nǐ, rén jiān duō huàn nán, shì yào ràng nǐ wán quán.</lyrics>
<title>rén de shēng mìng hé děng duǎn zàn 迦南696</title>
</song>